  "texts": [
    "The results of clinical trials show that approximately 90% of new active substances fail to gain regulatory approval due to poor efficacy and unexpected toxicity [5].",
    "Despite being developed and marketed successfully, drugs can be withdrawn if they cause side effects.",
    "Among the types of adverse drug reactions, DILI has been the leading cause of drug withdrawal and disapproval during drug discovery in recent decades [6][7][8].",
    "Therefore, early prediction and assessment of DILI are major challenges in drug development.In general, experimental animal models are used to predict DILI.",
    "However, they are time-consuming, laborintensive, and have poor concordance between species [9]."
  ],
